MAPPLET.DESCRIPTION: [07.11.2012:A.G] INC0569343_P05_Discrepancy in Retail Audit Facts Date. Correct the way timezone conversion is performed
MAPPLET.NAME: MPLT_TIMEZONE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT C.ROW_ID AS ROW_ID, SM.START_DATE AS START_DATE, SM.END_DATE AS END_DATE, SM.DST_BIAS AS DST_BIAS, TZ.UTC_OFFSET AS UTC_OFFSET FROM S_CONTACT C LEFT OUTER JOIN S_TIMEZONE TZ ON C.TIMEZONE_ID=TZ.ROW_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN WC_SUMMERTIME SM ON SM.TIMEZONE_ID=TZ.ROW_ID WHERE C.TIMEZONE_ID IS NOT NULL AND C.EMP_FLG='Y'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: ROW_ID = CONTACT_ID AND START_DATE <= INPUT_DT AND END_DATE >= INPUT_DT

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT S_TIMEZONE.UTC_OFFSET as UTC_OFFSET, S_CONTACT.ROW_ID as CON_ID FROM S_TIMEZONE(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN S_CONTACT(NOLOCK) ON S_CONTACT.TIMEZONE_ID=S_TIMEZONE.ROW_ID
